(Key Ideas To Remember) Tj
T*
(- Modern Physics should first be understood as a scientific principle before it is) Tj
T*
(treated as an exam topic.) Tj
T*
(- The learner must understand the main ideas and methods involved in Modern Physics) Tj
T*
(because it controls how questions in Modern Physics are answered correctly.) Tj
T*
